Create a new dictionnay from dictionnary key=>values:
just keep value number 'index' from all values.

```pycon
>>> data={10: ("dix", 100, "a"), 20: ("vingt", 200, "b")}
>>> createDict(data, 0)
{10: 'dix', 20: 'vingt'}
>>> createDict(data, 2)
{10: 'a', 20: 'b'}
```
